posting_body: ['A Brand-New High-End 39 Story Luxury High-Rise in the Victory Park Neighborhood with Panoramic Views of Downtown Dallas!!', 'Walking Distance to Many Upscale Restaurants, Shopping, Night-Life, and Entertainment!', 'Each Apartment Has Several Desirable Amenities, Such as Quartz Countertops, Stainless Steel Appliances, Gas Range Stove, Hardwood Floors, and Even a Built-In Wine Fridge!', 'Other Amenities Included; Spa Bathroom with a Stand-Up Shower and Oversized Soaking Tub, Walk-In Closet, Floor to Ceiling Windows, with a Full-Size Washer and Dryer Included.', 'These Beautiful Apartment Amenities Include a Luxurious Resort Lounge Pool with a Tanning Deck, a Wellness Center, a State of an Art Gym, and even a Park with a Pet Spa for Your Beloved Animals!', 'More Amenities Include a Golf and Sports Simulators, a Roof Top Lounge with Downtown Dallas Views, Plus So Much More!', 'These Luxury Apartments Even Include Climate Controlled Hallways, Parking Garage, Electric Vehicle Charging Stations, Personal Garages for Your Luxury Cars, and Elevators, What More Could You Ask For?', 'Most Importantly They Have Great Management, 24 Hour Concierge, and Maintenance!!', 'Please Contact Jacquelyn with Dash Realty at', 'show contact info', 'For More Information About This Breath-Taking Property.', '**12 Month Lease or Longer, No Corporate Leases, and No Sublease**']
